node.text: HIT THE LIKE BUTTON IF U BELIEVE IN YOURSELF‼️‼️‼️Life is crazy that’s all I can say... it’s been a Great week with with clients... Crazy to say that i literally invented the “package deal” I see a lot of people doing package deals now & all I can say is I support everyone to the fullest.. I’m so happy I created a wave and helped a lot go young kings see this music business in a different way! I can happily say I have had the last 10 months booked every single day with package deals.. this has been life changing and I am grateful and thankful to all my clients that have taken they’re time to fly to LA & work with us .. & shoutout to all the entrepreneurs out they’re getting it from the mud just like me.. this only the beginning ... and for all you people out there that doubt themselves please don’t! JUST BELIEVE IN YOURSELF THATS ALL I DID, LAW OF ATTRACTION IS REAL‼️🙏🏻❤️
